    public class Team
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Team>
    The class to represent a Team - A team has a 3 letter team code and a full team name. You only have a single private data member and you can't add anything to the class but you still have access to all the information you need
    NOTE: All parameters will be final and all preconditions will be checked
